<HSPACE=3D"12"><FONT color=3D#808080 face=3DTahoma font=3D"">
<P>A Lipid is a small parasite with an unusually large intelligence. A =
single=20
Lipid will live inside a host, unable to live outside a living being. =
</P>
<P>A Lipid offers it's host an improved life, the host will live longer, =
be more=20
able to combat other infections and have increased happiness. The Lipid =
has=20
evolved the ability to supply a variety of living beings these =
enhancements,=20
enhancing the immune system with it's own, slowing down cellular =
senescence and=20
controlling the balance of chemicals in a beings brain to control the =
level of=20
satisfaction. All that the host gives up is a small amount of free will. =
The=20
host becomes dedicated to the protection of it's parasite and usually =
other=20
Lipid hosts. The Lipid itself is capable of free thought and the host =
will 'make=20
decisions' partly of it's own and partly the Lipid's. The host is mostly =
unaware=20
that it has been manipulated in any way. </P>
<P>When a non host is exposed to Lipid hosts these life forms will often =
join=20
the Empire willingly, the improved quality of life and the helping hand =
of the=20
Lipid to motivate the individual to get the best out of their life is in =
many=20
cases a big enough draw to give up a small amount of free will. </P>
<P>Lipid's display a great desire to procreate, to bring new host bodies =
in to=20
their Empire. Not all life forms that enter an Empire controlled by the =
Lipids=20
will become hosts but many will, in the majority of cases voluntarily. =
This=20
makes a Lipid empire seem aggressive in it's decisions. </P>
<P>The Lipid's will try to improve the pool of hosts by cooperation with =
other=20
Empires also so they are a fairly trustworthy ally.</P>
<P>The Lipid's natural symbiotic relationship has allowed them to =
develop the=20
Lipid Host Center, allowing extremely fast and effective healing to any =
host=20
being a Lipid is able to live in.</P>
<P>The Lipid's preferred weapons are the Rail Gun, Area, and Ion and =
they have a=20
Balanced approach with Energy Research.</P></FONT></DIV></BODY></HTML>

